Package access.withdrawal

Class WithdrawalHandler

java.lang.Object
access.withdrawal.WithdrawalHandler
All Implemented Interfaces:
ApplicantWithdrawalFeatures, ManagerWithdrawalFeatures
public class WithdrawalHandler extends Object implements ManagerWithdrawalFeatures, ApplicantWithdrawalFeatures
Handles all withdrawal request operations in the BTO Management System. Implements interfaces for managers and applicants to provide role-appropriate access to withdrawal functionality and data.
